2014-07-22
Compatibility with Kohana 3.3
@ author Erwan Maire Choufourax
@ website wwww.upyupy.fr
@ webiste wwww.bwat.fr
----------------------------

1. Change files names case to match the file/class naming conventions
http://kohanaframework.org/3.3/guide/kohana/upgrading#psr-0-support-fileclass-naming-conventions

2. Change the call of debug function
http://kohanaframework.org/3.3/guide/kohana/debugging
// Deprecated :
echo Kohana::debug($akismet);
// replaced by :
echo Debug::vars($akismet);